text: Bhai tumhare liye to ek memoir nahi likha jaayga. Itne saare events hue tumhare saath ki I've lost count lol. Earliest memory is Shrey ko esc padhana and uske zada aa gaye loooool. Fir to Hovercraft bhi jeete the! And, "me as well don't know who you are" bhai ye nahi bhulega mujhe kabhi. 17k :p. yAaar ye sab bakchodiyan kahan chali gayin thi aage jaake. Main hi shayad alag ho gaya tha wing se. Memoir in progress to tumne likha complete main kar raha hun ye nahi chalega. Are and we also had the trip to lucknow, ghar bhi aaye the sab, how can I forget! The summer project, ghiste the har roz and fir wire se mast katna thermacol. Kitne bachpan ke din lag rahe yaar. I am happy ki fir se milne ka mauka mila hamen! Iski value aaj fir realize kar raha. Hope to see you soon.

text: Hey bro! It was so nice knowing you. 1st years summers saath mein ghise hain dono aero and fir dono bhaag gaye the lol. The Lucknow trip I will always remember, a fond memory. text: Hey Dweepak, I cannot let slide not writing a memoir for uu. 3 years of knowing you and has been amazing. Surprisingly we were neighbors in 1st year but didn't get to know each other much. Then it's been like woah! Partnered up in cs202, and that continued for each and every course (except cs251 sorey). But damn this is amazing. I never could appreciate that it's so looong. You have been an awesome friend (tackling the weight of emotional breakdowns of so many damn, including me). Man so many random times we've spent, I wish we could get more (at least the full share of last year). It is a small memoir, hardly does justice, I know, but make do till we meet again!

text: Roomie brooo! Maaf karna memoir jaisa likhna chahta tha, waisa mauka nahi mil raha. Yaar kitna mast samay raha hai ye journey. I have poor memory in general, but I still remember meeting you on first day of college. Abhi se match karunga to same nahi dekhoge, khair shayad us din shaant isliye the kyunki tumhare parents bhi the. I remember your medical box, usse iso propyl alcohol strip di thi tumne pehle hi dun kyunki maine ink faila di thi apne documents ya kapde pe, I remember not. Bhai kya 4 saal rahe hain ye. Kitna ghumte the 1st year mein, kitni bakchodi karte the. Stories kahin khatam hi nahi hoti. Astro club bhi kiya aur fir takneek hawa mein karke aa gaye the lol. Yaar chhoti chhoti yaaden, Smarth ke kamre pe ek baar darte hua gaye the 1st year mein, badminton khelna, mafia mast chapu admi the tum. Beating you at bluff in last sem will be one of my great achievements. Yaar light on/off ke jhagde haha. Aur 80% time to main tumko sota hua hi pata tha din mein :) Fir canteen pe dahi paratha khate the mast. Main to bas aise hi random yaaden stitch karte hue likh diya, inko bohot miss kar raha hun and karta rahunga. Bohot dukh hai ki aakhri saal maze poore nahi kar paaye. Lockdown mein baat-cheet khatam hi ho gayi thi bhala ho ark verma ka, firse saath mein kar diya. And jab campus wapasi hui to masttt. Bhai un teen hafton mein bhi jo pal beetain hai wo yaar bohot keemti the. Khoob maza kiya hai, and thodi asha hai ki thode aur mauke milenge. Milte hain firse, bhai 3 saal saath rahe ek doosre ko kahan se kahan jaate dekha hai.
author: Rohan  Gupta
